{"tid":1745473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角區選投票站附近驚現近50枚汽油彈","createTime":"2019-11-22T08:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T02:32:09.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"80ad833429dd2fb53512c7bc438a8f22eed8684a","tid":1745473,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:38:00.000Z","msg":"旺角洗衣街一條後巷發現大量汽油彈。<br />\n<br />\n現場是洗衣街239號旁邊一條橫巷，警方下午約3時接獲市民報案，指上址發現一批汽油彈。警員到場，將現場圍封調查。經點算後，初步證實有4盆汽油彈，每盆有10多枚，警方在場另檢獲多個空樽及仍未入樽的汽油。<br />\n<br />\n涉案現場對面是界限街1號體育館，周日將作為區議會選舉投票站，警方正追查該批汽油彈的來源及使用動機。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，有街坊早前曾看見有私家車及客貨車停泊，有人分批將汽油彈載至上址。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1643854/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E5%8D%80%E9%81%B8%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E7%AB%99%E9%99%84%E8%BF%91%E9%A9%9A%E7%8F%BE%E8%BF%9150%E6%9E%9A%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E8%AD%A6%E6%9F%A5%E4%BE%86%E6%BA%90%E5%8B%95%E6%A9%9F</code></pre>"},{"pid":"5a98d2f857f6ef28f2f72aec6353cdbf3b46e7a0","tid":1745473,"uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:38:20.000Z","msg":"popovan ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ec0b07bebe992f96aea6659c2ef874d30a169b","tid":1745473,"uid":167548,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:38:39.000Z","msg":"屌你老尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff51e4927e283b6812dfa3bee4aa73d01d55081a","tid":1745473,"uid":225977,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:38:56.000Z","msg":"次次前一兩日都咁啱捉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd57798bc793850be4fe735c41dde705e4691dea","tid":1745473,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:39:00.000Z","msg":"取消區選前奏？"},{"pid":"75ee54989fc374caaee7a94bd0913756977d5ac9","tid":1745473,"uid":166616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"